stories.title: 5th Match, ICC Knock Out, Pakistan v Sri Lanka, Statistical Highlights
stories.summary: It was the 1634th ODI in cricket history

stories.title: Pakistan humble Sri Lanka to reach the Semis
stories.summary: They say the most effective way of putting breaks on the opposition's run rate is to take wickets

stories.title: Pakistan cruise into ICC KnockOut semi-finals with win over weak Sri Lanka
stories.summary:
Saeed Anwar had a word with batting partner Yousuf Youhana moments before he
hit the  six which gave him a century and took Pakistan to a nine-wicket
victory over Sri Lanka in the ICC KnockOut 2000 quarter-final at the Nairobi
Gymkhana Club on Sunday

stories.title: Sri Lanka swept aside as Pakistan progress to ICC KnockOut semi-finals
stories.summary: Pakistan swept into the semi-finals of the ICC KnockOut tournament on the back of an assured century from Saeed Anwar as Sri Lanka were brushed aside by nine wickets at the Nairobi Gymkhana Club on Sunday

stories.title: Pakistan cruise to victory over Sri Lanka
stories.summary:
An opening stand of 90 between Saeed Anwar and Imran Nazir set Pakistan up
for a semi-final berth in the ICC KnockOut tournament as last year's World
Cup finalists cantered after a winning target of 195 on Sunday

stories.title: Pakistan give themselves excellent chance of beating Sri Lanka
stories.summary: Pakistan gave themselves an excellent chance of reaching the ICCC KnockOut semi-finals by restricting Sri Lanka to a moderate total of 194 in their quarter-final clash at the Nairobi Gymkhana Club on Sunday

stories.title: Sri Lanka face uphill struggle
stories.summary:
Sri Lanka lost a succession of key top-order wickets as they reached 108 for
five after 25 overs in their ICC KnockOut quarter-final against Pakistan at
the Nairobi Gymkhana Club on Sunday

stories.title: Sri Lanka win toss and bat against Pakistan in ICCKnockOut
stories.summary:
Sri Lanka won the toss and elected to bat on a cool and overcast morning in
their ICC KnockOut quarter-final match against Pakistan at the Nairobi
Gymkhana Club on Sunday
